b"You can be whatever you wanna be. And don't let the fear from others make you question or doubt your inner light. Ok I'm done. \xe2\x9d\xa4\xef\xb8\x8f"

b'AND THE GREATEST GIFT GOD HAS GIVEN US IS THE GIFT OF FREE WILL. There is a choice.'
b'From the moment we were born we have been learning.'
b"You have to have the negatives so u appreciate the lessons they teach you. It's the balance."
b"People are afraid to be who they truly are because they limit themselves to other people's standards."
b'We are born and taught how to behave, think and it limits us. Society is controlled by fear.'
b'Can everyone see how the world is falling apart? Everyone so separate and afraid. The world brands us and labels shit to associate it with'
b'That is what makes you YOU. Faith and hope are sometimes misused by greed and envy. LOVE is the goal!'
